description:
Julian`s code name in cyber space is "Pluto". He is the only male type Third except D`anclaude. He has no idea why Dr. Asakura would create a male Third and considers himself created as a joke. Armitage is surprised to find there is a male type Third During their investigation and treats him like her younger brother.
Most of Julian`s profiles remain unknown but he is able to access most any computer`s core unit.
He sacrificed his "life" to save Armitage and later lives in cyber space with other Thirds killed by D`anclaude.
name: Julian Moore
